1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to revenue and taxation; to amend sections
2 60-3,185, 77-202.23, and 77-202.24, Reissue Revised Statutes of
3 Nebraska; to change a motor vehicle tax exemption and a property tax
4 exemption relating to certain disabled veterans; to harmonize
5 provisions; to provide an operative date; and to repeal the original
6 sections.
7 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
